{{Quote|I don't remember learning to read, but the first thing I remember reading is a science fiction novel.|Vonda N. McIntyre|<ref>''[[A Book Excerpt: The Crystal Star]]''</ref>}}
'''Vonda N. McIntyre''' was the author of ''[[The Crystal Star]]'',<ref name="TCS" /> as well as a number of ''Star Trek'' books and other original novels. She also wrote short stories and poems, and was a contributor to the blog [http://blog.bookviewcafe.com Book View Cafe]. She passed away on [[April 1]], [[2019]], after a short battle with pancreatic cancer.

